{"tid":2518080,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人同我一樣應該冇得靠父幹買樓","createTime":"2021-05-05T19:47:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T19:47:43.000Z","uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"86024a35092c5e728d3d2d94ef0316e523dd532e","tid":2518080,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T19:47:43.000Z","msg":"28歲 單身 儲蓄接近800K<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屋企96年左右入咗第一間 跟住過幾年再換過間就住到而家 原本層樓放租 點知撞正樓市暴跌 又聽講遇過租霸 09-10左右一賺少少就放咗第一間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住年年不停FF啲樓會暴跌 我近幾年開始儲錢想買樓有個私人空間 知道QE後啲樓跌得咁勁 一傾就嘈 佢話啲樓跌返幾成先肯資助我買樓 咁嘅價位唔值得買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我應該冇得靠父幹買樓了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}